      </hedline>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>Brian Schweitzer did not discuss the environmental impacts of turning half of the beautiful state of Montana into an open-pit coal mine and then converting the mined coal into atmospheric carbon dioxide.</p>
        <p>The solutions to our energy crisis are conservation and renewable energy.</p>
        <p>Michael J. Ellenbecker  Lowell, Mass., Oct. 3, 2005</p>
      </block>
